Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.87,0:00:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  不是这样的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.19,0:00:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  但你胸部肯定变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.36,0:00:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好恶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.49,0:00:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别留下你们劣等的遗传因子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些性欲旺盛的淫兽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.62,0:00:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  这是Bilbilder？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  女人真的都是低能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.96,0:00:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  但是很像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.36,0:00:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴唇也这么粗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你这么说  开学习班的老头子也是Bilbilder了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.60,0:00:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.68,0:00:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.15,0:00:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.26,0:01:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天的野兽  相当的凶猛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.51,0:01:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.60,0:01:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间也要吃盐味拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.60,0:01:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}（「芽间」音同「面码」，面码为干笋，常用于拉面佐料）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.12,0:01:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸡蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.33,0:01:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间要拌鸡蛋  拌鸡蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.59,0:01:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.43,0:01:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸡蛋要凝固了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.47,0:01:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸡蛋拌开来  拌开来  拌开来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}嗯？  拉面？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.20,0:01:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔来啦  打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.61,0:01:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}不错啊  仁太帮我也做一份
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.93,0:01:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.13,0:01:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  可以
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.58,0:01:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶  好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.36,0:01:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}为什么就给叔叔做  芽间却没得吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.09,0:01:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这对什么都说可爱的习惯  可以改掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.71,0:01:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前  芽间的小书库他也说可爱了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}这不是很好吗  对啥都能用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.02,0:01:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般不用的好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.07,0:01:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸡蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.01,0:01:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放一个  别搅碎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.47,0:01:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对叔叔偏袒  偏袒  太偏袒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.21,0:01:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视电视
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.92,0:02:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫猫好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.27,0:02:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸则是一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.53,0:02:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.03,0:02:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.33,0:02:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡椒  胡椒…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.15,0:02:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间也要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.31,0:02:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.24,0:02:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}筷子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筷子在哪  筷子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你怎么了  在家里中暑？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.81,0:02:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然可爱  但很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.21,0:02:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.97,0:02:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.47,0:02:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太很危险哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然仁太抓的最大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.80,0:03:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  好厉害好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候的我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  鹤子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.84,0:03:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有病  绝对的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定是积累已久的精神压力  积累已久的精神创伤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.06,0:05:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为夏天的炎热而产生形体…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.52,0:05:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  似乎还和青春期的性冲动相关
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假设
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我精神压力具现化的产物  存在于此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  为什么现在才出现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:06:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  还以成长后的状态出现
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你问我这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.23,0:06:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  芽间应该是想实现一个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.99,0:06:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么愿望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.28,0:06:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连愿望的内容都不知道还怎么实现啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我只是有这个感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.58,0:06:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说真的  到底为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喷口水了  真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.84,0:06:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防护壁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}这家伙是夏天的野兽  我的精神压力  我的精神创伤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.72,0:06:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是无敌的防护壁  这下芽间无敌了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.55,0:06:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有反防护壁的办法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  你先回忆下自己的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.28,0:06:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  关于这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.79,0:06:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的愿望是要大家一起才能实现的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.79,0:06:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.99,0:06:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  门铃在响啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去又能干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.18,0:07:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之乖一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.15,0:07:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}长大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又没着急
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.76,0:07:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么感觉肩膀好重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣  看不见芽间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.57,0:07:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.74,0:07:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师托我交给你的暑假作业
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.78,0:07:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假？  我说你已经两天…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和宿海不一样  我忙得很
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.02,0:07:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这东西随便丢掉不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.11,0:07:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我也不打算再去那垃圾学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.01,0:08:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算宿海不来  我也没所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.89,0:08:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你这样子很丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.00,0:08:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太大傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不拜托安鸣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「希望你和我一起实现愿望  安鸣」像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先和你说一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再叫她安鸣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}（「安鸣」和「肛门」同音）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要叫就叫安城或者鸣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.60,0:08:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.75,0:08:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣就是安鸣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对大家很好  还有很多游戏漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.07,0:08:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.61,0:09:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已经不是那时候的安鸣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算去求那死三八  她也绝对不会帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.81,0:09:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死三八？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.64,0:09:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是笨女人的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之她已经不是朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.86,0:09:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  我讨厌说安鸣坏话的仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  再去一次安鸣那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去拜托她吧  仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.66,0:09:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.48,0:09:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去拜托一下安城  你应该也会明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是安城
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.80,0:09:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在和以前已经完全不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.53,0:09:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  仁太还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.66,0:09:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帽子加眼镜？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  不是要去么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.70,0:10:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  购物吗  去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.16,0:10:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.28,0:10:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸好怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙齿上沾了拉面里的葱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.35,0:10:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别烦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  安鸣家不在这边哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便散散步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.56,0:11:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里以前是泡泡店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成瓦当劳了  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.59,0:11:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是芽间  还是喜欢土豆饼汉堡…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.41,0:11:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}那俩人以前和我一个中学的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.24,0:11:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那电影看了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个电影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.50,0:11:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是  会出来外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.72,0:11:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用双截棍的阿姐在学校里战斗的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.39,0:11:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也理所当然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然那三八给了我错觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其实没人会在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安城也说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.38,0:11:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不在乎我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}扯断头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.49,0:11:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是一成不变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是幻觉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.59,0:11:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现愿望么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.43,0:12:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这果然是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于芽间的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.85,0:12:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛  很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.70,0:12:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太  芽间她…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁…仁太？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.06,0:12:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.21,0:12:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.84,0:12:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.89,0:12:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.17,0:13:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  鸣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去过小仁家了没
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敲门
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我没敲么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.93,0:13:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管这了  说正经的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便去看了下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说这不关妈妈的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有关啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想让你带包子去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.85,0:13:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己带去不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青春期啊青春期
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.05,0:13:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢人的…是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.29,0:13:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.83,0:13:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑期讲习班刚回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹是个升学高中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.73,0:13:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本该我也穿上的高中校服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}倒是  你怎么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:13:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.07,0:13:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.48,0:14:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.21,0:14:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集和鹤子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.09,0:14:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  芽间她…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说错  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么芽间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在说这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.08,0:14:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.65,0:14:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中考失败
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进了这附近最低端的高中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不去学校  喊着本间芽衣子的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑子不正常了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.31,0:14:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集你这傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:15:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你兴奋什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一提到本间芽衣子  人就会变样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点你也一样吧  松雪同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.46,0:15:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别烦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没男子气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.99,0:15:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸蛋倒还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑袋也不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.74,0:15:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.26,0:15:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.50,0:15:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下你也明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.34,0:15:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都变了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.80,0:15:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  变化最大的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太  呐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.68,0:15:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的精神压力  差不多饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.19,0:15:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.02,0:16:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会想起好多好多恶心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.53,0:16:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我烦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.53,0:16:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候  那时候的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.02,0:16:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样子的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.24,0:16:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么决定了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们  超和平Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Busters？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思好像就是强大的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.28,0:16:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来保护和平
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.14,0:16:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}哪里的和平？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.42,0:16:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论什么地方  各种和平
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.61,0:16:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  仁太就是队长喽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.01,0:17:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都跟在我后面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.89,0:17:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  仁太是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢芽间的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.82,0:17:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说老实话吧  超和平Busters里不许有隐瞒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.12,0:17:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说  说  说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.44,0:17:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说呀  说呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁…谁会喜欢这丑八怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为她会哭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为芽间是爱哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.66,0:17:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.73,0:18:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.17,0:18:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去下妈妈那里  饭在微波炉里转一下再吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.31,0:18:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那笑容  让我一直挂念在心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当时想明天再道歉就行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.54,0:18:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.04,0:18:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那个明天  永远没有到来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.47,0:18:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.91,0:18:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  门开了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就关上呗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.39,0:19:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小聪  长大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸呢  有好多白发
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.67,0:19:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.94,0:19:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小聪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.42,0:19:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次吃咖喱都要给姐姐一份  看着好碍眼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  这是姐姐最喜欢吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.79,0:19:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了就吃不了东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样子说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.83,0:19:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐有点呆呆的地方  可能还不知道自己已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.39,0:19:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己已经死了的事  芽间还是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.19,0:19:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊  杯子自己倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快收拾掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.39,0:20:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.67,0:20:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  又不是我干的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.88,0:20:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.05,0:20:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美地破坏了和平的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不知不觉中渐渐离散
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.63,0:20:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间要拌鸡蛋  拌鸡蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.16,0:20:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙会去的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.08,0:21:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想要  那一天的第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想要能向芽间道歉的第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.75,0:21:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.78,0:21:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的精神压力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.91,0:21:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的精神创伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.06,0:21:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为了向芽间道歉而生出了芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.70,0:21:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样  就不能这么下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.59,0:22:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.55,0:22:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么搞的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.84,0:22:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也…太高手向了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.25,0:22:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜  和正常向的差距才是浪漫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.94,0:22:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  这不是仁太么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.90,0:22:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗噗…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.38,0:22:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  就在这刻名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.89,0:22:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「超」怎么写？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.63,0:22:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.15,0:22:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左边写个「走」…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.94,0:22:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「走」怎么写？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.88,0:22:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.05,0:22:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}（超和平Busters）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.28,0:22:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天  在这里停止的时间又开始流动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.05,0:22:54.26,eden,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Dear love...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.55,0:22:58.86,eden,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Your charms alone are beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.98,0:23:02.60,eden,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Can you be my dear love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.92,0:23:07.05,eden,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I'll hold your hand I'll hold your arms
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.16,0:23:13.50,eden,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}'Til the end of time Will you be mine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.61,0:23:19.38,eden,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}This love is climbing over sunrise
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.61,0:23:23.56,eden,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Over the moon slides
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.79,0:23:27.83,eden,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}So when the wind blows
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.01,0:23:30.35,eden,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I'll seal this love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.46,0:23:37.11,eden,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Until the end of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.14,0:23:44.45,eden,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Dear love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.63,0:23:48.94,eden,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Your charms alone are beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.09,0:23:52.83,eden,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Can you be my dear love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.03,0:23:56.69,eden,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I've come to know that chances
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.80,0:24:00.83,eden,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Fall into the sand
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.32,0:24:03.69,eden,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Please understand
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.79,0:24:09.22,eden,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}You've brought the girl inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.70,0:24:15.44,eden,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Inside of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.26,0:24:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  芽间的等级还那么低啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.16,0:24:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.11,0:24:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…爸爸基本不让我玩游戏啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.87,0:24:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢  我是躲在厕所里偷偷玩布袋妖怪的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.13,0:24:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在厕所里玩啊  真臭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.03,0:24:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜…呜…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.31,0:24:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  骗你的骗你的  不臭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.09,0:24:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的  别哭了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.86,0:24:47.36,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(215,270)\fad(400,0)}勇者芽间


